Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:18.11,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, in a crazy dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:20.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was gazin' up to the Promised Land
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:24.82,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らのユメの形　ザワメキ出す Heart！ Beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.82,0:01:26.83,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on let's go to that place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:28.79,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stop anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:33.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛びだせ　仄暗い空　fly into the light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:37.46,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じたいこの世界に生まれたことが幸せってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:40.06,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新時代へ続く扉を開けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:42.31,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:45.81,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なぁ、わかってるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.74,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らはいつだって傷だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:50.93,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみのルーツ断ち切って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:54.64,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怖くないよ　いつでも傍に感じるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:57.33,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　もっと　もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:02:01.79,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い　力が心満たしてく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.86,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.24,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake！ Up！ Your！ Heart！ Beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:09.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blazeに生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:11.53,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ感じて Burning！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:13.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brave and boiling heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:16.03,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絆を示せ High！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blazeに生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:20.32,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ感じて Burning！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:21.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Boost！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:22.65,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real deal！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:23.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No more liars
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:24.90,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ignition's ON, my heart is on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:26.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fire Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My blood will burn on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:31.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah fight on！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:18.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我还是个孩子 在一个疯狂的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:20.19,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正仰望着那块约定之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.19,0:01:24.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的梦的形状 喧嚣四起 心脏起跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.82,0:01:26.83,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让我们共同前往那块土地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:28.79,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.04,0:01:33.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳跃吧 穿过白日阴沉 飞入光芒 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:37.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信出生于这个世界是一件幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.46,0:01:40.06,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开通往新时代的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:42.31,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:45.81,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你是知道的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.52,0:01:48.74,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:50.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力斩断悲伤的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.41,0:01:54.64,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕 我们永远能在身边感受到彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:57.33,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 更多 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.62,0:02:01.79,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将更多炙热的力量填满心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒你的心跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:09.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:11.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动  燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:13.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢而沸腾的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:16.03,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现彼此的羁绊 高涨！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:20.32,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动  燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:21.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速到极限！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:22.65,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是来真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:23.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要更多谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:24.90,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置已点火 心脏已起搏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:26.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰 火焰 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:28.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的热血将燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:31.27,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开战吧！
